{"tid":2065653,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"咁多人講smile/lasik，但無人講smart TPRK？","createTime":"2020-06-15T17:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T14:35:53.000Z","uid":57005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"89b73f18655678fcdd2364407ecb701857581de0","tid":2065653,"uid":57005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T17:10:16.000Z","msg":"本身想做smile，搵post睇做下research果時，見到有人提過smart TPRK<br />\n<br />\n睇完覺得好似正過smile，係康復期耐D<br />\n但發現原來台灣有咗幾年，香港完全無聲氣，主流都係smile<br />\n<br />\n再搵下資料，原來香港&quot;好似&quot;有，但同lasik放埋一類，所以無人留意？<br />\n<br />\n見之前都有幾個巴打提過smart TPRK，有人仲話想去台灣做<br />\n想問下有無人真係做過，講下意見感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42377a6b8f16168b7236a04b5f499e46023d044e","tid":2065653,"uid":132374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T17:27:47.000Z","msg":"Google完好似好正咁，但好似揾唔到香港有？"},{"pid":"d46bf48f5d0e1efc81d0967860343a40b3ce05ca","tid":2065653,"uid":357203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T17:36:01.000Z","msg":"我係做呢隻，但唔喺香港做"},{"pid":"5f68c296dfaeed21a11bcfd7fc6ead6996daf660","tid":2065653,"uid":57005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d46bf48f5d0e1efc81d0967860343a40b3ce05ca","tid":2065653,"uid":357203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T17:36:01.000Z","msg":"我係做呢隻，但唔喺香港做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T01:21:47.000Z","msg":"台灣？終於搵到香港人做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以講下過程同感受？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9a4f00f02bb8c1b24d0a6df6ecf3c695072dc1","tid":2065653,"uid":220779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T01:22:43.000Z","msg":"養和有得做 不過康復期真係好耐"},{"pid":"17fc1203ab0ef0b354008d564070bbdda3a3c694","tid":2065653,"uid":57005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c9a4f00f02bb8c1b24d0a6df6ecf3c695072dc1","tid":2065653,"uid":220779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T01:22:43.000Z","msg":"養和有得做 不過康復期真係好耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T01:32:17.000Z","msg":"養和無寫係咪smart，所以我唔肯定<br />\n<br />\n我睇台灣就話3-4日有8成左右，可以返工<br />\n比SMILE要請多幾日假<br />\n<br />\n幾隻手術各有好處啦<br />\n但後遺症好似TPRK少D，定係少人做無咁多人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba881c628594305fbbc71af6082629d41937c1c","tid":2065653,"uid":50674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T01:38:34.000Z","msg":"同lasek (唔係lasik) 有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fcc33bc9692f416ca588b5105988d52afb86b78","tid":2065653,"uid":57005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ba881c628594305fbbc71af6082629d41937c1c","tid":2065653,"uid":50674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T01:38:34.000Z","msg":"同lasek (唔係lasik) 有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T03:38:56.000Z","msg":"根據<a href=\"https://mulicia.pixnet.net/blog/post/27826245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmulicia.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F27826245&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7phbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=3e41477c\" target=\"_blank\">https://mulicia.pixnet.net/blog/post/27826245</a>(有手術圖，慎入）<br />\nlasek係開角膜上皮再激光，完咗蓋返埋<br />\ntprk 直接laser走角膜皮<br />\n<br />\nLASEK利用經過稀釋的酒精軟化角膜上皮與下層組織相連的部份，再揭開角膜上皮，用激光打磨，最后蓋上角膜上皮，遮蓋傷口，用以減低痛楚與傷口的反應。手術后，原有的角膜上皮會逐漸被新生的上皮細胞取代。<br />\n無瓣全激光角膜切削術（TPRK）則在角膜地形圖引導下，以激光取代人手操作來去除角膜上皮，切割的精準度及均勻程度都大大提升，疼痛比傳統的PRK手術明顯減少、上皮愈合亦較快，現時愈來愈多眼科醫生采用TPRK。"},{"pid":"ce3a7bea6ba9544ed16f80855a3b7954349ba0e5","tid":2065653,"uid":357203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17fc1203ab0ef0b354008d564070bbdda3a3c694","tid":2065653,"uid":57005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c9a4f00f02bb8c1b24d0a6df6ecf3c695072dc1","tid":2065653,"uid":220779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T01:22:43.000Z","msg":"養和有得做 不過康復期真係好耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T01:32:17.000Z","msg":"養和無寫係咪smart，所以我唔肯定<br />\n<br />\n我睇台灣就話3-4日有8成左右，可以返工<br />\n比SMILE要請多幾日假<br />\n<br />\n幾隻手術各有好處啦<br />\n但後遺症好似TPRK少D，定係少人做無咁多人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T04:35:22.000Z","msg":"如果無寫smart要注意下，因為Smart prk同普通prk有啲唔同"},{"pid":"bc98321920d23bc2fc2e639b988349432f0c881e","tid":2065653,"uid":357203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f68c296dfaeed21a11bcfd7fc6ead6996daf660","tid":2065653,"uid":57005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d46bf48f5d0e1efc81d0967860343a40b3ce05ca","tid":2065653,"uid":357203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T17:36:01.000Z","msg":"我係做呢隻，但唔喺香港做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T01:21:47.000Z","msg":"台灣？終於搵到香港人做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以講下過程同感受？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T04:38:07.000Z","msg":"喺北美，本身喺呢邊住緊<br />\n我揀呢隻係因為佢係做完之後完全冇傷口， smile個傷口細但都唔係完全冇，睇你自己衡量<br />\nRecovery 比smile, lasik慢<br />\n<br />\n做嗰陣其實冇咩感覺，淨係望住啲光就OK<br />\n我好似要成三四日先恢復八成視力，啱啱做完就好似你冇戴眼鏡嗰陣咁朦<br />\n一星期後視力完全正常"},{"pid":"ca4132a968613a4c73e384f192a45d9950fea356","tid":2065653,"uid":57005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc98321920d23bc2fc2e639b988349432f0c881e","tid":2065653,"uid":357203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f68c296dfaeed21a11bcfd7fc6ead6996daf660","tid":2065653,"uid":57005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d46bf48f5d0e1efc81d0967860343a40b3ce05ca","tid":2065653,"uid":357203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T17:36:01.000Z","msg":"我係做呢隻，但唔喺香港做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T01:21:47.000